quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,When the earth is shaken with her shaking
  99,2,and the earth yields up her burdens
  99,3,"and man says, “What ails her?”"
  99,4,That Day she shall convey her chronicles
  99,5,for thy Lord inspired her
  99,6,That Day mankind shall issue forth upon diverse paths to witness their deeds
  99,7,So whosoever does a mote’s weight of good shall see it
  99,8,And whosoever does a mote’s weight of evil shall see it